 mbrown42@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  
     
       
     
           
                           
                 
                 
                                       
                                   
               
                        
           
                          Feb. 4 (Bloomberg) -- David Woo, global head of foreign-exchange strategy at Barclays Capital, talks with Bloomberg's Scarlet Fu about the outlook for the dollar and factors contributing to its market valuation.
     Woo also discusses the euro, the possible impact of European Central Bank and Bank of England monetary policy on investor sentiment and the performance of some emerging market currencies. (Source: Bloomberg)  
                           

     
